 "remarks": "Dramatic Contemporary Colonial with soaring ceilings, hardwood floors, sun-drenched large rooms with open floor plan. Eat-in kitchen has Bosch double convection oven, glass cooktop, newer frig &amp; newer washer/dryer. Huge living room with wood-burning fireplace, high ceilings, skylights &amp; windows abound! Separate formal dining room &amp; additional separate family room create easy flow for today&apos;s living &amp; entertaining. Private deck off the dining room allows for quiet relaxation sipping morning coffee, evening cocktails &amp; BBQing over-looking 1.6 peaceful, quiet, private acres surrounded by beautiful property &amp; stonewalls. Upstairs invites you into the primary ensuite bedroom with walk-in closet plus 2 other closets, some w/built-ins &amp; bath w/whirlpool tub, walk-in shower, glass door &amp; double sinks. Additionally there&apos;s an office/computer/library area on the upstairs landing w/separate upper loft. Partially finished lower level provides more lifestyle options, i.e. exercise gym/recreation area/extra office space &amp; storage. Central air plus 2-car garage. Minutes to schools, shopping, commuting, beaches. Fantastic rental home! Owner may consider pets - Ask.",
